originalText.text:
I honestly suggest getting your teeth extracted here. My four wisdom teeth were removed in a relatively short amount of time. I was sedated, so there was absolutely no pain during the procedure. After the procedure, when I woke up, I felt confused, dizzy and even nauseous. However, the care I got from the x-ray tech in particular was excellent. She helped me sit down and waited with me until I felt well again.

Since the waiting time is extremely long, I would strongly advise anyone going to this location to arrive earlier than 7am. Additionally, They don't really explain how to properly care for the surgical site, all they give you is a piece of paper with instructions, so be sure to READ carefully and conduct further research on how to properly care for the extraction site.

originalText.text: I have struggled with going to the dentist my entire life. So I made the decision to go to an oral surgeon to be put to sleep. Unable to get an IV for the anesthesia I called it quits from fear. He was soooo patient with me, I literally cried like a baby for over 40 minutes and he just would not give up on me when I gave up on myself. I begged him to just forget about doing me and move on to his next patients. He wouldn't needless to say he got me through it, with the amount of time I wasted crying and saying I couldn't find it in myself he found it in me. I can not stress enough the reviews I have seen on here was absolutely nothing at all what I experienced. I'll never see another dentist besides him EVER!! Him, the nurse's were the absolute best. Believe me when I tell you that the bad reviews are complete and utter nonsense I advice you coming from a big sissy give him a try you won't regret it. Thanks again from the bottom of my heart!!!

originalText.text: Visiting a Dentists can be very intimidating and in occasions scary and expensive, but I have to say that from the moment that I made the appointment I felt very comfortable and secure. I was having difficulty finding a dentist that would help me with my emergency and that participated with my insurance.The staff was amazing and got me in the office immediately. Dr Quintana was so supportive and professional,he explained everything that he was going to do and walked me through the whole process, making me feel safe and relax,I wasn't nervous at all knowing that I was in good hands. I felt no pain and before I knew it,i was on my way home. I would definitely recommend him to my friends and family.
